title: HOUR 3- Collin Morikawa 081120
itunes:title: HOUR 3- Collin Morikawa 081120
description:
PGA Championship Winner Collin Morikawa tells Dan that he celebrated his first major tournament win by not sleeping all night while having a few drinks and eating a couple in-and-out burgers. Collin says that he thought he could win the whole thing during and after Saturday's round of golf.
